  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    org.springframework.beans.factory.Aware, org.springframework.beans.factory.BeanNameAware, org.springframework.context.ApplicationContextAware, org.springframework.web.context.ServletContextAware, org.springframework.web.servlet.View

    @Component(value="cas3ServiceJsonView")
public class Cas30JsonResponseView
extends Cas30ResponseView
    Renders the model prepared by CAS in JSON format. Automatically sets the response type and formats the output for pretty printing. The class relies on MappingJackson2JsonView to handle most of the model processing and as such, does not do anything special. It is meant and kept to provide a facility for adopters so that the JSON view can be augmented easily in overlays.
    Since:
    4.2
